.TP 9n
u
Update the library.
.TP 9n
i
Toggle colors derived from album cover or from color theme.
.TP 9n
v
Toggle spectrum visualizer.
.TP 9n
b
Switch between ascii and image album cover.
.TP 9n
r
Repeat current song after playing.
.TP 9n
s
Shuffles the playlist.
.TP 9n
a
