.TP 9n
Shift+Tab
Switch to previous view.
.TP 9n
Backspace
Clear the playlist.
.TP 9n
Delete
Remove a single playlist entry.
.TP 9n
t,g
Move a song up or down the playlist.
.TP 9n
number + G or Enter
Go to specific song number in the playlist.
.TP 9n
Esc or q
Quit
\fBkew\fR.
